{
  "stem": "17001.8",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 222.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as we were sitting there, I feel that somebody is trying to grab me, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I look up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I see a hairy hand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I jumped up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said to my sister, let's get the hell out of here, because they are trying to catch us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we ran away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know if they caught any of the other girls, but we ran away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We ran up to the hill where we were the night before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said to myself that this is impossible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, you don't have peace.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You don't have to be afraid of the gas chamber, but now they want your body.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So finally there was a train that was going through [POLISH] from Praga.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So there were full of Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we were standing outside on the step.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I couldn't sit down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I-- I don't know how I did it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If I take the wrong move, the wheel would take off my leg for sure.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So finally, we get to [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In [POLISH], as we are sitting at the station, my sister was exhausted.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were exhausted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were sitting there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was standing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She was sitting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There comes a Russian soldier, and he opens his flies, and he throws my sister down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he's ready to lay on her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got so angry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know where I got my nerve.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I pushed him off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to my sister, you stupid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Get up.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And jump up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What-- what are you sitting there for?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What are you waiting for?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the soldier, as he was trying to get up, I gave him a slap.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That he-- he just shook up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I started hollering.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said to the people there, who were at this railway station.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
